title: China's car exports surged in 2025, but domestic demand slowed
description: HONG KONG (AP) — China’s auto exports surged 21% in 2025, driven by rising shipments of electric vehicles, while domestic demand slowed, an industry association said Wednesday.

title: Delay in reviewing Sabah's 40% revenue share will undermine court ruling, says SLS
description: KOTA KINABALU: Delaying the High Court‐directed review of Sabah's entitlement to 40% of net federal revenue derived from the state will undermine the judicial decision as well as the Constitutional process itself, the Sabah Law Society (SLS) says. Read full story
